{"id":2041,"date":"2012-09-01T14:04:16","date_gmt":"2012-09-01T14:04:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/?p=2041"},"modified":"2013-01-21T08:51:31","modified_gmt":"2013-01-21T08:51:31","slug":"uk-backstage-catering","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/uk-backstage-catering\/","title":{"rendered":"Artist Catering and Riders for bands including Razorlight, The Feeling and Texas."},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Another great event catering job <strong>Red Radish<\/strong> handled during the course of\u00a0 summer 2012 was to supply the artist backstage catering and alcohol <a title=\"Riders explained\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2012\/01\/backstage-riders-explained-by-the-smoking-gun\/\"><strong>riders<\/strong><\/a> at a music festival in <strong>Hampshire. <\/strong>Bands included Razorlight, The Feeling, Magic Numbers and Texas and as usual\u00a0their management company were delighted with not only the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2010\/05\/fish\/\"><strong>great food<\/strong><\/a> but also our friendly service. Bands tend to travel with quite an entourage including production, sound and\u00a0 lighting plus often a large bunch of family and friends who all need looking after and feeding. It is often an an ever-changing requirement that requires not only an adaptable team but also <strong>meticulous planning<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2050\" title=\"vegemite-logo\" src=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/vegemite-logo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"438\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/vegemite-logo.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/vegemite-logo-300x219.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\"><strong>Timing, privacy, quality and enthusiasm<\/strong><\/a> are all also essential in making sure (sometimes) demanding artists and band members are 100% happy and ready to sing their hearts out. Rock stars and warm beer are not after all two likely bed-fellows so every detail needs to be totally perfect and usually in a situation where the most basic of equipment is often not quite to hand . We however <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2012\/06\/experienced-festival-caterer-ideal-for-backstage-bands-and-crew\/\"><strong>love the challenge<\/strong><\/a> of keeping everyone happy as we try to juggle the rest of the crew\u2019s requirements around the lead-singers passion and express wishes for a Vegemite sandwich and an ice cold bottle of Brazilian Skol beer at being delivered to his dressing room at exactly 7.43 in the evening. That is after all Showbiz!<\/p>\n<p>See exactly what <strong>Joe Malik of 24:7 Media and Events <a title=\"Client Reference from Joe Malik\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2012\/09\/uk-backstage-catering-at-its-best\/\">thought about Red Radish<\/a><\/strong><a title=\"Client Reference from Joe Malik\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2012\/09\/uk-backstage-catering-at-its-best\/\">.<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Another great event catering job Red Radish handled during the course of\u00a0 summer 2012 was to supply the artist backstage catering and alcohol riders at a music festival in Hampshire&#8230;. <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/uk-backstage-catering\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2047,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2041","post","type-p